Frances L. Allen



Ms. Frances L. Allen is President at Jack in the Box, Inc. and Brand Marketing Officer at DD IP Holder LLC.
Ms. Allen was previously employed as Independent Director by MarineMax, Inc., Chief Brand Officer & Executive Vice President by Denny's Corp., Chief Brand Officer & Executive Vice President by Denny's, Inc., Chief Marketing Officer by Dunkin' Brands, Inc., Vice President-Marketing by Sony Mobile Communications, a Director-International Advertising by Frito-Lay North America, Inc., and Senior Vice President by DMB&B Worldwide.
She received her undergraduate degree from The University of Southampton.



